It would be great to bulk-manage versions (archieve, delete, etc).
&nbsp;
----

h4.REST API Workaround
{panel}
This KB article on [How to bulk release versions through REST API in Jira|https://confluence.atlassian.com/jirakb/how-to-bulk-release-versions-through-rest-api-in-jira-1027124117.html], published on Nov 2 2020, offers a {{curl}}/REST API alternative to bulk edit versions in Jira.
It's focused on 'releasing versions' but can be adjusted to update other versions' fields.
{panel}

If I enter the HTML enitity code for a non-breaking space:
{noformat}&nbsp;{noformat}
JIRA does not escape the ampersand, so the text appears as a literal space (&nbsp;). This only affects the Wiki field renderer.

