Currently, the {{SearchService}}'s {{getIssuesFromFilter()}} does not limit the number of returned issues like the one supported by {{getIssuesFromTextSearchWithProject()}}. It will be so annoying if the result has 1000+ issues, or even better, if you can set the {{startRow}} and {{endRow}}.

